{"metadata":{"kernelspec":{"language":"python","display_name":"Python 3","name":"python3"},"language_info":{"name":"python","version":"3.12.12","mimetype":"text/x-python","codemirror_mode":{"name":"ipython","version":3},"pygments_lexer":"ipython3","nbconvert_exporter":"python","file_extension":".py"},"kaggle":{"accelerator":"none","dataSources":[],"dockerImageVersionId":31328,"isInternetEnabled":true,"language":"python","sourceType":"notebook","isGpuEnabled":false}},"nbformat_minor":4,"nbformat":4,"cells":[{"cell_type":"markdown","source":"#  Challenge 3\n\n### **1. The Concept: \"Midnight Monolith\"**\nThe **Midnight Monolith** is a fictional, invitation-only fashion exhibition set in an underground, brutalist concrete gallery in Dubai. This project uses Generative AI to bridge the gap between cold, industrial environments and the fluid geometry of high fashion.\n\n### **2. The Mood: \"Brutalist Noir\"**\nTo ensure a cohesive visual identity, the design follows a strict set of aesthetic guidelines:\n\n* **Visual Palette:** Absolute Monochromatic (**Greyscale**). No mid-tones or colors are used, to emphasize shadow and light.\n* **Lighting:** **High-Contrast Chiaroscuro**. Sharp transitions between deep obsidian blacks and glowing ivory whites to create a sense of mystery and prestige.\n* **Atmosphere:** **Minimalist & Editorial**. The mood is cold, silent, and expensive—evoking the feeling of an empty, high-end concrete gallery before a show.\n* **Geometry:** **Symmetrical & Linear**. The use of leading lines (as seen in the runway concepts) to draw the viewer’s eye toward a central focal point.\n\n### **3. Design Intent**\nThe goal of this poster is to act as a \"Visual Anchor\" for the AI-generated fashion collection. Every design decision—from the stark white border to the centered, capitalized typography—is intended to reinforce the feeling of an elite, AI-driven future for the fashion industry.","metadata":{}},{"cell_type":"code","source":"# Cell 1: Install required libraries\n!pip install -q diffusers transformers accelerate","metadata":{"trusted":true,"execution":{"iopub.status.busy":"2026-04-07T17:41:33.428201Z","iopub.execute_input":"2026-04-07T17:41:33.428445Z","iopub.status.idle":"2026-04-07T17:41:38.118183Z","shell.execute_reply.started":"2026-04-07T17:41:33.428424Z","shell.execute_reply":"2026-04-07T17:41:38.117271Z"}},"outputs":[],"execution_count":1},{"cell_type":"code","source":"import torch\nprint(f\"Is CUDA available? {torch.cuda.is_available()}\")\nprint(f\"Current device: {torch.cuda.current_device() if torch.cuda.is_available() else 'No GPU detected'}\")","metadata":{"trusted":true,"execution":{"iopub.status.busy":"2026-04-07T17:41:41.719021Z","iopub.execute_input":"2026-04-07T17:41:41.719290Z","iopub.status.idle":"2026-04-07T17:41:44.833159Z","shell.execute_reply.started":"2026-04-07T17:41:41.719264Z","shell.execute_reply":"2026-04-07T17:41:44.832203Z"}},"outputs":[{"name":"stdout","text":"Is CUDA available? False\nCurrent device: No GPU detected\n","output_type":"stream"}],"execution_count":2},{"cell_type":"code","source":"import torch\nfrom diffusers import StableDiffusionPipeline\nimport matplotlib.pyplot as plt\nfrom IPython.display import display, Markdown\n\n# 🛠️ THE FIX: Smart Device Detection\nif torch.cuda.is_available():\n    device = \"cuda\"\n    torch_dtype = torch.float16\n    print(f\"🚀 Great! GPU detected: {torch.cuda.get_device_name(0)}\")\nelse:\n    device = \"cpu\"\n    torch_dtype = torch.float32\n    print(\"⚠️ GPU not detected. Running on CPU (This will be slow, but it won't crash).\")\n\nprint(\"Loading Stable Diffusion Model...\")\nmodel_id = \"runwayml/stable-diffusion-v1-5\"\n\n# Load the pipeline with extra safety flags\npipe = StableDiffusionPipeline.from_pretrained(\n    model_id, \n    torch_dtype=torch_dtype,\n    low_cpu_mem_usage=True\n)\npipe = pipe.to(device)\n\nprint(f\"✅ Model successfully loaded on {device.upper()}\")","metadata":{"trusted":true,"execution":{"iopub.